Project Name: 
Mnemonic Translator

Outline: 
Create a cross-platform mobile application that can validate a Mnemonic phrase and translate it from one language to another.

Language & Tools: 
	•	TypeScript

MVP Functionalities:
	•	Validate mnemonic phrases.
	•	Translate mnemonic phrases to another language.
	•	Create algorithm for mapping indexes of Mnemonic phrases during translation.

Extra Functionalities:
	•	Create front-end UI for mnemonic phrase validation.
	•	Create front-end UI for mnemonic translation between supported languages.
